name: General Purpose Hicet - GREEN
description:
This  GREEN Hicet token was originally issued by Huw Messie in consolation for fucking up the first mint of "Piercing Strand Theory" on September 25, 2021 at 1:20pm EST, as collectors were frantically refreshing the page in order to place their offers as fast as humanly possible.

The initial purpose of this token is to entitle its owner the ability to preorder a future artwork of 26 editions. However, ownership does not hold any guarantee and tokens are only to be used for record keeping and sentimental purposes.

*** Contact Huw Messie via Twitter @huwythechew, Email huwmessie@gmail.com, or Instagram @huwmessie before attempting to cash-in this token to confirm its validity. ***

This token is general purpose, and may be traded or reissued by Huw Messie for future instances of similar consequence.

Hicet tokens are transferable.
